category: STOCKS & INVESTMENTS
category comment: 

clue: Munis are one type of these debt securities issued by many governments

response: (municipal) bonds

clue: Also used in a different type of gambling, this colorful term describes a stock with a history of paying out

response: a blue chip stock

clue: This alliterative event occurs when a company repurchases its own stock, increasing the value of the remaining shares

response: a buyback

clue: A rule that halts trading in the case of a sudden decline is called this, like a switch that trips to stop an electric overload

response: a circuit breaker

clue: Basic goods like grains, beef & oil are traded as these & usually sold as derivative contracts called futures

response: commodities

